<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="historicalAndRevision" id="idb9961aa6-47c4-11f1-9a61-b1559996dfe8"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Historical and Revision Notes</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Based on <ref href="/us/usc/t28/s101">section 101 of title 28</ref>, U.S.C., 1940 ed., Judicial Code and Judiciary (<ref href="/us/act/1911-03-03/ch231/s40">Mar. 3, 1911, ch. 231, § 40</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/36/1100">36 Stat. 1100</ref>).</p>
</note>
